headline: Industrial Packaging Stocks Q2 Teardown: Packaging Corporation of America (NYSE:PKG) Vs The Rest
summary: The end of an earnings season can be a great time to discover new stocks and assess how companies are handling the current business environment. Let’s take a look at how Packaging Corporation of America (NYSE:PKG) and the rest of the industrial packaging stocks fared in Q2.
